description: Welcome to 9 W Broadway -- a gorgeous condo in the Court Square Press Building! This rarely available unit stack is a 2 bed 2 bath with a stunning open concept living room and kitchen with brand new cabinets and dishwasher. The exposed brick and beams mixed with all the modern touches makes this feel like true Boston living. Equipped with granite countertops, new appliances, new hot water heater, upgraded W/D in unit, Australian hardwood floors, central AC & heat, PLUS 1 garage parking spot! The second bedroom has a beautiful, unique barn door to allow for extra light to flood the room. This luxury building includes 24/7 concierge, fully equipped gym, professional screening room, prep kitchen, pool and outdoor grilling on the 4th floor terrace. Situated in between the South End and South Boston with a close walk to Seaport -- just steps to Whole Foods and the T! In addition, there is also easy guest/visitor parking in the back of the building, perfect for weekends!
